00:32:57,925 --> 00:32:58,475
Baik.

727
00:33:00,416 --> 00:33:02,541
Ini barulah perempuan yang sepadan
dengan pengarah kita.

728
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:04,166
Perempuan tadi...

729
00:33:04,416 --> 00:33:05,083
Teruklah!

730
00:33:06,541 --> 00:33:07,208
Tunggu sebentar.

731
00:33:14,875 --> 00:33:15,625
Yin Sichen!

732
00:33:17,083 --> 00:33:18,333
Mereka harus ambil gambar seperti ini,

733
00:33:18,833 --> 00:33:21,833
barulah karya itu layak dapat 99 markah.

734
00:33:33,166 --> 00:33:33,958
Apa yang awak nak buat?

735
00:33:37,416 --> 00:33:38,250
Apa yang saya nak buat?

736
00:33:38,250 --> 00:33:39,541
Saya nak minum air, tak boleh?

737
00:33:50,458 --> 00:33:51,750
Saya dah minum air ini tadi.

738
00:34:07,700 --> 00:34:09,375
♪Oh yeah♪

739
00:34:13,050 --> 00:34:15,518
♪Ada tak seseorang♪

740
00:34:15,625 --> 00:34:20,150
♪Buat aku suka sehingga rindu♪

741
00:34:24,166 --> 00:34:25,375
Yin Sichen, apa yang awak nak buat?

742
00:34:26,333 --> 00:34:27,208
Samseng teruk!

743
00:34:31,708 --> 00:34:33,041
Sayalah samseng teruk?

744
00:34:33,041 --> 00:34:33,625
Ya.

745
00:34:34,775 --> 00:34:36,916
Awak dah lupa apa yang telah
awak buat malam tadi?

746
00:34:36,958 --> 00:34:38,125
Apa yang saya buat malam tadi?

747
00:34:44,675 --> 00:34:45,541
Maaf kerana mengganggu.

748
00:34:46,333 --> 00:34:47,375
Hantar Cik Gu pergi.

749
00:34:54,458 --> 00:34:55,708
Awak memotong kereta saya

750
00:34:55,750 --> 00:34:57,291
dan menyebabkan kereta saya dilanggar.

751
00:34:57,291 --> 00:34:58,791
Inilah resit pembaikan, sila bayar.

752
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:00,541
Awak dah gila kerana fikirkan wang?

753
00:35:01,875 --> 00:35:03,583
Adakah awak anggap semua di dunia ini

754
00:35:03,583 --> 00:35:04,875
mata duitan seperti awak?

755
00:35:06,916 --> 00:35:08,375
Kelak, fikirkan alasan yang baik

756
00:35:09,125 --> 00:35:09,958
sebelum jumpa saya.

757
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:11,125
Awak...

758
00:35:18,750 --> 00:35:19,708
Yin Sichen!

759
00:35:21,583 --> 00:35:22,375
Tengoklah nanti.

760
00:35:50,250 --> 00:35:51,000
Sichen.

761
00:35:53,916 --> 00:35:54,625
Xiwei.

762
00:36:03,625 --> 00:36:05,125
Ubah ikut pelan ini saja.

763
00:36:05,125 --> 00:36:05,833
Ini.

764
00:36:05,833 --> 00:36:06,333
Baik.

765
00:36:07,041 --> 00:36:08,041
Encik Alex.

766
00:36:09,075 --> 00:36:11,208
Saya ada sesuatu nak minta bantuan
daripada awak.

767
00:36:37,580 --> 00:36:40,380
♪Seperti meteor berlalu♪

768
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:44,260
♪Menerangi langit malam♪

769
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:47,780
♪Aku tak sanggup biar kamu♪

770
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:51,220
♪Jatuh dalam sekelip mata♪

771
00:36:52,020 --> 00:36:55,100
♪Jalan berliku-liku♪

772
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:58,580
♪Tapi cahaya berkelip-kelip♪

773
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:02,140
♪Sebab percintaan♪

774
00:37:02,140 --> 00:37:05,980
♪Pernah wujud dengan benar-benar♪

775
00:37:07,140 --> 00:37:10,260
♪Kalau detik itu ulang lagi♪

776
00:37:10,740 --> 00:37:14,100
♪Aku takkan berundur♪

777
00:37:14,420 --> 00:37:19,180
♪Tertarik olehmu sepanjang masa♪

778
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:24,420
♪Sebab aku, hati jadi kosong♪

779
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:28,420
♪Teguh dan tidak berpura-pura♪

780
00:37:28,980 --> 00:37:33,500
♪Hanya mahu beri kamu
segala yang terbaik♪

781
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:36,420
♪Di dunia♪

782
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:39,780
♪Aku yang cinta padamu♪

783
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:43,660
♪Cerita dongeng memang benar♪

784
00:37:45,020 --> 00:37:46,780
♪Sayangku yang datang tepat pada masa♪

785
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:51,020
♪Adalah sudut yang lembut dalam hatiku♪

786
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:54,220
♪Kita saling menawan♪

787
00:37:54,660 --> 00:37:58,220
♪Mudah lagi tekad♪

788
00:37:58,740 --> 00:38:02,500
♪Impianmu jadi lebih lengkap♪

789
00:38:02,500 --> 00:38:05,820
♪Kuat dan tabah♪

790
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:09,380
♪Demi kita♪

791
00:38:09,420 --> 00:38:13,100
♪Cinta memecahkan peraturan♪

792
00:38:14,580 --> 00:38:16,900
♪Sebab percintaan kita perlukan♪

793
00:38:16,900 --> 00:38:20,620
♪Cahaya dan haba masing-masing♪

794
00:38:20,980 --> 00:38:23,580
♪Lindungimu secara diam-diam♪

795
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:27,580
♪Serahkan segalanya kepadaku♪

796
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:32,180
♪Menjelma jadi galaksi♪

797
00:38:32,180 --> 00:38:35,180
♪Di langit malamku♪

798
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:39,100
♪Tidak jatuh selama-lamanya♪

